14:23.197 --> 14:25.403
- I can't. It's too emotional.
- Okay. Some other time.

14:25.490 --> 14:26.819
- I was 10.
- Oh, God.

14:26.909 --> 14:28.486
Dressed as Quasimodo,
on a front porch...

14:28.577 --> 14:31.531
