14:35.584 --> 14:37.909
- Timmy took the entire bucket and put it in his bag.
- Mmm.

14:38.003 --> 14:40.838
Timmy didn't play by the rules.
It's what I liked and feared about him.

14:40.923 --> 14:42.915
- Oh.
- Then the bag broke.

14:43.008 --> 14:46.342
As a crowd of kids rounded the corner,
saw the pile of candy...

14:46.428 --> 14:48.136
