16:31.783 --> 16:35.698
Thank you for joining us
on our special night.

16:35.787 --> 16:39.239
Other children haven't fared so well.

16:39.333 --> 16:42.334
Oh, help me. Help me.

16:42.419 --> 16:46.464
  Welcome to your nightmare.
Ha, ha, ha, ha.

16:46.548 --> 16:48.624
Now your treats are over here...

16:48.717 --> 16:54.222
but with all the fog,
