18:52.132 --> 18:53.591
Look, here's the thing.

18:53.675 --> 18:55.419
We-We have fireworks
at Christmas now...

18:55.511 --> 18:57.135
because that's what they do in Colombia.

18:57.221 --> 18:58.715
I don't mind.

18:58.805 --> 19:00.597
Thanksgiving...
That used to be me roasting a turkey...

19:00.682 --> 19:03.387
until the gays took it over
with whatever new turkey cooking craze...

19:03.477 --> 19:06.229
it is that you saw on the Food Network,
and I'm fine with that too.

19:06.313 --> 19:11.224
All I ask... all I ask...
is that you leave me Halloween. Yeah, Halloween.

19:11.318 --> 19:15.067
I realize it is a crazy-ass holiday for a
grown woman to care about this much...

19:15.155 --> 19:17.397
but it is <i>my</i> crazy-ass holiday.

19:18.492 --> 19:19.986
Mine.

19:27.042 --> 19:28.785
That's a lot of complaining
from somebody...

19:28.877 --> 19:31.712
who asked for thirds
of our tandoori turkey last year.

19:34.299 --> 19:35.414
- Claire...
- No!

19:35.509 --> 19:36.968
No, not ready to talk!

19:37.052 --> 19:39.210
- No.

19:39.304 --> 19:40.799
Listen.

19:41.974 --> 19:43.800
I know I haven't been much help today.

19:43.892 --> 19:47.724
That whole Jerry and Judy thing,
it really hit me hard.

19:47.813 --> 19:49.805
Is that why you've been
acting like such a nut all day?

19:49.898 --> 19:52.140
- You know, what if someday that's us?
- Honey...

19:52.234 --> 19:54.939
Look, you might not want
to hear this right now...

19:55.028 --> 19:56.653
after the meltdown I just had in there...

19:56.738 --> 20:00.190
but you're kinda stuck with me.

20:01.368 --> 20:03.574
- You promise?
- Oh.

20:05.914 --> 20:07.373
- I do.

20:11.712 --> 20:14.333
Trick or treat!

