and she goes...

21:03.096 --> 21:04.295
"Cam, what's wrong?

21:04.389 --> 21:05.884
You look like a deer in head lice."

21:07.059 --> 21:09.217
In the service, I had a job...

21:09.311 --> 21:11.932
briefly... handling explosives...

21:12.022 --> 21:14.347
which sounds dangerous, but it's not.

21:14.441 --> 21:15.900
You store them at the right temperature...

21:15.984 --> 21:17.479
you have no problems...

21:17.569 --> 21:19.194
If you tell her she
doesn't have a choice...

21:19.279 --> 21:22.066
she'll say,
"Don't you give me an old tomato."

21:22.157 --> 21:24.565
- Or when she's...
- Okay, enough!

21:24.660 --> 21:26.237
You try speaking in another language!

